<HEAD>Dollar Trades Lower in Japan; Share Prices Gain</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: LEADS throughout to UPDATE with closings. No pickup.</HEAD>
<DATELINE>TOKYO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The key index on the Tokyo Stock Exchange reached a
