   The man reportedly told police after the breakdown that it was
futile for him to remain a fugitive.
   Photographs of the robber in action were taken by surveillance
cameras in Helsinki banks. Witnesses reported seeing a white car
with the steering wheel on the right side, bringing the vehicle to
the attention of the police.
   The robber has criminal record in Britain, the reports said.
