<SECOND>PM-OPEC, 3rd Ld-Writethru, f0050,0805</SECOND>
<HEAD>Oil Ministers Resume Negotiations</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: RESTORES dropped PM cycle designator; SUBS lead to change Monday
to today to conform to style</HEAD>
